@startuml
title Viaverse Payment / Wallet — State Diagram

[*] --> CREATED
CREATED --> PENDING : provider session created
PENDING --> AUTHORIZED : provider success
AUTHORIZED --> CAPTURED : capture/settle
PENDING --> FAILED : provider failure
PENDING --> CANCELLED : expired/cancelled
CAPTURED --> REFUND_REQUESTED : refund requested
REFUND_REQUESTED --> REFUNDED : approved + provider refund

CAPTURED --> PAYOUT_HELD : job not completed yet
PAYOUT_HELD --> PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE : job completed/no dispute
PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE --> PAYOUT_RELEASED : admin/system release
PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE --> PAYOUT_BLOCKED : dispute/risk
PAYOUT_BLOCKED --> PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE : resolved

FAILED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]
PAYOUT_RELEASED --> [*]

note bottom
Payment status and payout status are related but separate.
Disputes block payout without necessarily changing captured payment state.
end note
@enduml
